      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">8</infon>
        <offset>1076</offset>
        <text>In addition, biomass partitioning of the emergent multitrophic community is consistent with well-established empirical norms in the surface oceans.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">9</infon>
        <offset>1224</offset>
        <text>At steady state, ecosystem fluxes can be probed to characterize the effects that viruses have when compared with putative marine surface ecosystems without viruses.
</text>
