      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">10</infon>
        <offset>1389</offset>
        <text>The model suggests that ecosystems with viruses will have (1) increased organic matter recycling, (2) reduced transfer to higher trophic levels and (3) increased net primary productivity.
</text>
