      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">11</infon>
        <offset>1577</offset>
        <text>These model findings support hypotheses that viruses can have significant stimulatory effects across whole-ecosystem scales.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">12</infon>
        <offset>1702</offset>
        <text>We suggest that existing efforts to predict carbon and nutrient cycling without considering virus effects are likely to miss essential features of marine food webs that regulate global biogeochemical cycles.
</text>
      </sentence>
